job.title: HPCL Advisor Recruitment 2021   Apply online for Various  Vacancies in Mumbai
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Posts:

  • Biomass Advisor

Description

New Central Government Jobs have been published by Hindustan Petroleum Limited for the vacancies of Biomass Advisor. If you are finding a government job in Mumbai then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Mumbai, from 23.04.2021, and till 24.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Mumbai and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification to apply for HPCL Biomass Advisor vacancies in Mumbai:

  • To apply for a Biomass Advisor posts Mumbai, your B.E/B.Tech, B.Sc, MTech, MBA, BBA must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these vacancies is the 23.04.2021
  •  The last date to apply for these vacancies is 24.05.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 30 to 60 years old. 

HPCL Biomass Advisor Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for title.

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of these vacancies in Mumbai

Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of HPCL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY HPCL
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
